text: It doesn't matter which type of creature it is as long as it has orange color it is wudsy. All of the other colors are not.
So, a creature can be yellow or blue or pink, if it has orange parts it is wudsy.
okay, so orange is wudsy, and any other color (purple, blue, yellow) is not wudsy
